{"tid":2433283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁振英: 是否如果不愛黨，就可說成不愛國。","createTime":"2021-03-05T00:14:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T02:28:15.000Z","uid":185631,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8042cc52396502660b97758aacadb12199e5f304","tid":2433283,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:14:18.000Z","msg":"正在北京準備出席全國兩會的梁振英，以視像訪問方式接受本台專訪，他強調愛國者治港的原則和目標完全是天經地義。<br />\n<br />\n他批評香港有立法會議員跑到外國，要求對方制裁自己國家和香港，形容此行為聳人聽聞，不愛國家，亦危害國家利益。雖然香港已落實《香港國安法》，但梁振英認為，若果香港沿用現時的選舉制度及方式，這批人可能在下一屆仍會當選，出現外國的傀儡進入治港班子，這是絕不能接受，因此需要完善選舉制度，堵塞漏洞，確保最後的選舉結果做到愛國者治港。<br />\n<br />\n至於參選者要愛國是否亦要愛黨，梁振英認為提出討論這些問題的人是轉移視線，形容是「攞嘢嚟講」。他質疑為何要劃分愛國與愛黨的界線，反問是否如果不愛黨，就可說成不愛國。<br />\n<br />\n另外，近日有政務官被批評未符合愛國者治港標準，梁振英說，不評論個別情況，至於特首應具備甚麼條件才可以應付現時的社會狀況，他重申要求是要愛國、愛港。<br />\n<br />\n對於如何看有建議取消超級區議會議席，但會否予人民主倒退的感覺，梁振英表示，超級區議會的歷史好短，強調世界很多地方都會因應實際情況，改變選舉制度，因此不用對改變選舉制度而感驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578668-20210304.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578668-20210304.htm&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUoc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=7bf3f5cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578668-20210304.htm&h=6999f7c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578668-20210304.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1609f6fad7808fa63170219f32e011aae0b02107","tid":2433283,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/v9-3c_IdQGnFkwS5QOgT8GN6kRg=/4825x2714/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PN3MB2WHEND7XGBXYNDYCWHE6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fv9-3c_IdQGnFkwS5QOgT8GN6kRg%3D%2F4825x2714%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPN3MB2WHEND7XGBXYNDYCWHE6Y.jpg&h=33f55f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/03141528/image1614752123140.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F03141528%2Fimage1614752123140.png&h=daf48570&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99e771883023e9bcd9a42384b80f3f759365e0f7","tid":2433283,"uid":248576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:18:22.000Z","msg":"呢期佢咁活躍又想做多次特首？"},{"pid":"c309a73f311d35d630bfd40ddc149c7a98fa60b6","tid":2433283,"uid":55010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:21:48.000Z","msg":"忠誠反反對派咪就係愛國不愛黨"},{"pid":"75687665dc2a855aa0f98ade404c1ad26543870e","tid":2433283,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c309a73f311d35d630bfd40ddc149c7a98fa60b6","tid":2433283,"uid":55010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:21:48.000Z","msg":"忠誠反反對派咪就係愛國不愛黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:23:24.000Z","msg":"即係佢哋條路行唔通啦"},{"pid":"38fcfae2893c91bd7956e8aa9fed2d62154423ef","tid":2433283,"uid":364767,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:25:20.000Z","msg":"好心689搵番份正經嘢做，例如<br />\n『掃地，企枱，洗廁所，雞頭，甚至做鴨...』<br />\n點都有骨氣過做西環喉舌 咁下賤吖！"},{"pid":"bed91de330437c454aa0a8ac3977a367b1140d83","tid":2433283,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:27:02.000Z","msg":"廢老又鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f282dfd2cf43503ecbf5dcdcb39ad38372355daf","tid":2433283,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:35:34.000Z","msg":"忠誠的廢物 (失業）"},{"pid":"b252598d6ccbdf61718ada99fb18b915c70ed4b9","tid":2433283,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:37:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">六四屠殺真相我只信梁振英</span></span><img src=\"/assets/fac